  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272480/extras/592e5e6c9d3f770388a56e58d4b0603c.avif?t=1723754219\" width=500 height=252 /></span><br><br><strong>Gninja Pig is a platformer 2D game with pixel art</strong>. A unique dose of cuteness with movements and attacks to take on challenges. Humans disappeared after a mysterious disaster, so you have to survive on your own but maybe you’ll find allies in your adventure.<br>Avoid traps, fight or avoid enemies, complete objectives and mostly, have fun.<br>Guinea Pig animations created exclusively for the game, and this game is developed only by me.<br><br>Guinea Pig owners will recognize references to guinea pig life and other people could just enjoy the parkour and combat of this game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Release Date Is Approximately Middle 2023.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272480/extras/4ddf80f4e90a0fdebd8e1ad69cc31851.poster.avif?t=1723754219\" width=512 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272480/extras/4ddf80f4e90a0fdebd8e1ad69cc31851.webm?t=1723754219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272480/extras/592e5e6c9d3f770388a56e58d4b0603c.avif?t=1723754219\" width=500 height=252 /></span><br><br><strong>Gninja Pig is a platformer 2D game with pixel art</strong>. A unique dose of cuteness with movements and attacks to take on challenges. Humans disappeared after a mysterious disaster, so you have to survive on your own but maybe you’ll find allies in your adventure.<br>Avoid traps, fight or avoid enemies, complete objectives and mostly, have fun.<br>Guinea Pig animations created exclusively for the game, and this game is developed only by me.<br><br>Guinea Pig owners will recognize references to guinea pig life and other people could just enjoy the parkour and combat of this game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Release Date Is Approximately Middle 2023.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272480/extras/4ddf80f4e90a0fdebd8e1ad69cc31851.poster.avif?t=1723754219\" width=512 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272480/extras/4ddf80f4e90a0fdebd8e1ad69cc31851.webm?t=1723754219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
